OL,3,CMan dies and several injured after car
OL,4,Ccrashes during police pursuit
OL,6,FA man has died and several people have
OL,7,Fbeen seriously injured after a vehicle
OL,8,Finvolved in a police pursuit crashed
OL,9,Fin East Sussex.
OL,11,FSussex Police said that a BMW collided
OL,12,Fwith three other vehicles on the A21
OL,13,Fin Robertsbridge at about 8.20pm on
OL,14,FSaturday.
OL,16,FThe driver of the BMW involved in the
OL,17,Fpursuit, a 23-year-old man from
OL,18,FHailsham, died at the scene. His
OL,19,Ffamily has been told.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
