CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776041702
OL,3,CMan dies and several injured after car
OL,4,Ccrashes during police pursuit
OL,6,FTwo passengers in another vehicle were
OL,7,Ftaken to hospital with serious
OL,8,Finjuries, while several other people
OL,9,Finvolved sustained minor injuries
OL,10,Frequiring hospital treatment.
OL,12,FThe A21 has been closed while
OL,13,Finvestigations are carried out.
OL,15,FAs the BMW had been involved in a
OL,16,Fpolice pursuit shortly before the
OL,17,Fcollision, a referral was made to the
OL,18,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,19,Fwho will conduct an independent
OL,20,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
