PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776041702
OL,3,CMan dies and several injured after car
OL,4,Ccrashes during police pursuit
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Andy
OL,7,FWolstenholme said: "This was a tragic
OL,8,Fincident, and our thoughts are with
OL,9,Fthe family of this young man and all
OL,10,Fthose affected.
OL,12,F"An investigation is underway to
OL,13,Funderstand the full circumstances and
OL,14,Fthere will be increased police
OL,15,Factivity in the area while this is
OL,16,Fongoing.
OL,18,F"I would like to thank the public for
OL,19,Ftheir patience during the emergency
OL,20,Fresponse and for their understanding
OL,21,Fas our enquiries continue.
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
